## Cork board for SF circular metal end table

Call 888-208-4848 and ask for cork board without backing. This will result in 1/4 inch instead of 1/2 inch thickness.

[https://www.walldecorsuperstore.com/MT100-Round-Mounted-Cork-Circle-P6610.aspx](https://www.walldecorsuperstore.com/MT100-Round-Mounted-Cork-Circle-P6610.aspx) 

15 inch diameter round cork board for $23, free shipping.
